      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a solid start, really captures the tone. Can you make it even more specific though? Maybe add a part where he's describing their physical appearance or their customs in a way that makes them seem even more \"uncivilized\" compared to Europeans. Like, he's looking at their village or their way of life and realizing how much they \"lack\" compared to what a proper society has. It would add more tension to the scene.",
